         <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <t:note>The following excerpts are taken from the edition <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/97TNCJ8U"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:MalkaGubae1974"/><title level="m">መልክዐ ጉባኤ &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;(&lt;/hi&gt;Mälkǝʾa gubaʾe&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, 'Collection of hymns')&lt;/hi&gt;</title><pubPlace>ʾAśmarā</pubPlace><publisher>Kokaba Șǝbāḥ māttamiyā bet</publisher><date>1981</date><t:citedRange unit="page">16–19</t:citedRange></t:bibl>.</t:note>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="1">
                  <t:l n="1">ቅድስት፡ ወብፅዕት፡ በልሳነ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘነፍስ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ስብሕት፡ ወቡርክት፡ በአፈ፡ ዐቢይ፡ ወንኡስ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ዘየዓውደኪ፡ ሞገሰ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">ተሰመይኪ፡ ሥምረተ፡ አብ፡ ወማኅደረ፡ ወልድ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">ወምጽላለ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ መንፈስ፡</t:l>
               </t:lg>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="13">
                  <t:l n="1">ለኪ፡ ይደሉ፡ ለአግብርትኪ፡ ወለአእማትኪ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ትስአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ኀበ፡ ወልድኪ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ እመ፡ መላኪ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">በዝ፡ ማኅሌት፡ ወበውዳሴ፡ ሶበ፡ እጼውዕ፡ ስመኪ፡</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">አንብርኒ፡ በልብኪ፡ ጥሪተ፡ እኩንኪ፡</t:l>
               </t:lg>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
         
      </t:body>
